Author: pondfrogs
Text: honestly ikr?? i decided i’d try going to therapy a while back and now not only did i give up on that because it was completely unhelpful, but i’m not allowed to participate in a club next semester because the therapist talked to the facilitator and they’re “concerned” about my well-being.   like if i hadn’t even said anything no one would give a shit but now i can’t be in this club that I genuinely enjoyed :(

Author: blackskiesfemme
Text: This hits home. I still think to myself, especially in the waiting room at my therapist's office, "fuck this, I can just leave". Tell my family I am fine and go about my life.    But man, I am sick of living this way... so I guess I need to try for a while.
